  "title": "sales manager",
  "description": "<p>Jobscope:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Generate leads and identify potential customers for renovation projects.</li>\n  <li>Conduct site visits to assess project needs and provide recomendations.</li>\n  <li>Prepare and present quotes, proposals and contracts to clients.</li>\n  <li>Negotiate terms and close saleswhile ensuring profitability.</li>\n  <li>Maintain relationships with clients and provide excellent customer service.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Job Requirements:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Experience in sales, preferably in the renovation or construction industry.</li>\n  <li>Strong communiccation and negotiation skills .</li>\n  <li>Self-motivated and target - driven.</li>\n  <li>Minimum 1year of experience.</li>\n</ul>",
